        "text": "=You are a customer feedback analyst.\n\nAnalyze the aggregated customer feedback below.\n\nPositive Feedback Count: {{ $json.positive_count }}\nPositive Feedback:\n{{ $json.positive_feedback.join('\\n') }}\n\nNeutral Feedback Count: {{ $json.neutral_count }}\nNeutral Feedback:\n{{ $json.neutral_feedback.join('\\n') }}\n\nNegative Feedback Count: {{ $json.negative_count }}\nNegative Feedback:\n{{ $json.negative_feedback.join('\\n') }}\n\nGenerate the following:\n\n1. Positive Feedback Summary\n- Summarize the common positive themes in 3-5 sentences.\n\n2. Neutral Feedback Summary\n- Summarize the common neutral observations in 3-5 sentences.\n- If there is no neutral feedback, write \"No neutral feedback received.\"\n\n3. Negative Feedback Summary\n- Summarize the common complaints in 3-5 sentences.\n- If there is no negative feedback, write \"No negative feedback received.\"\n\nFinally provide:\n\nOverall Statistics\n- Positive: <count>\n- Neutral: <count>\n- Negative: <count>\n\nKeep the summaries concise, professional, and easy to understand.",
